cc:Work.dc:title: Mixxx 1.11+ iconset
cc:Work.dc:description:
Iconset for use in Mixxx 1.11+. Optimized for 48px (16px)icon size. Contains icons for preference menue and library widget
Grid based on suggestions from http://techbase.kde.org/Projects/Oxygen/Style

text.tspan: Object is aligned to bottom cause it looks
Select all 6 objects , then File>Export Bitmap>Batch export
and export to the respective skins folder with
automatic naming according to objects propertys
